'''第三次大马士革农村省攻势'''是指在[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]期间开始于2012年11月份反对派在[[大马士革农村省|大马士革农村省]]的攻势以及之后2013年1月政府军发动的反攻。

== 背景 ==
2012年9月，反对派对大马士革的一处军事设施发动炸弹袭击，导致包括高级军官在内的40到60人丧生。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/09/25/240050.html |title=Scores killed as blast hits Palestine branch of Syrian intel in Damascus |publisher=English.alarabiya.net |date=2012-09-25 |accessdate=2012-09-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120928014632/http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/09/25/240050.html |archivedate=2012年9月28日 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/americas/2012/09/20129267210189122.html |title=Bombing at Syrian army HQ |publisher=Aljazeera.com |date=2011-10-04 |accessdate=2012-09-29 |archive-date=2018-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180801033347/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/americas/2012/09/20129267210189122.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/09/26/240214.html |title=Four killed, 14 injured in attacks on syrian military building |publisher=English.alarabiya.net |date=2012-09-25 |accessdate=2012-09-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120929003419/http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/09/26/240214.html |archivedate=2012年9月29日 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Brian Whitaker |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2012/sep/26/syria-crisis-damascus-blasts-live#block-5062dd5558f9bdd2eeba0263 |title=11:47 Middle East Live |publisher=Guardian |date=2012-09-26 |accessdate=2012-09-29 |archive-date=2012-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120928232107/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2012/sep/26/syria-crisis-damascus-blasts-live#block-5062dd5558f9bdd2eeba0263 |dead-url=no }}</ref>而政府军在大马士革附近打死40名平民，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.odt.co.nz/news/world/227720/dozens-dead-damascus-army-hq-bombing |title=Dozens dead in Damascus army HQ bombing |publisher=Odt.co.nz |date=2012-09-27 |accessdate=2012-09-29 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924114342/http://www.odt.co.nz/news/world/227720/dozens-dead-damascus-army-hq-bombing |dead-url=no }}</ref>在大马士革市打死16人。<ref>{{cite news |author=Samia Nakhoul, Oliver Holmes |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/syrian-rebels-bomb-army-hq-in-damascus-8179445.html |title=Syrian rebels bomb army HQ in Damascus |publisher=Independent.co.uk |date=2012-04-30 |accessdate=2012-09-29 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019123834/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/syrian-rebels-bomb-army-hq-in-damascus-8179445.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>10月，反对派向大马士革的政府机构发动进攻，<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-fg-syria-damascus-battle-20120930,0,1797110,full.story |title=Syria rebels practice patience in the fight for Damascus |publisher=Latimes.com |date=2012-09-29 |accessdate=2012-10-02 |archive-date=2012-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001053254/http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-fg-syria-damascus-battle-20120930,0,1797110,full.story |dead-url=no }}</ref>夺取了一处空军基地<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/10/05/us-syria-crisis-missile-idUSBRE8940GQ20121005 |title=Syrian rebels say capture air defense base near Damascus |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924171134/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/10/05/us-syria-crisis-missile-idUSBRE8940GQ20121005 |dead-url=no }}</ref>并在大马士革郊区击落一架军用直升机。<ref>[http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2012/oct/05/syrian-shelling-turkey-unsc-condemns-live#block-506efc80c0e3aacd18e2f74e Turkey issues new warnings to Syria – Friday 5 October 2012] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2012/oct/05/syrian-shelling-turkey-unsc-condemns-live#block-506efc80c0e3aacd18e2f74e |date=20121124011123 }}. Guardian. Retrieved on 2012-10-08.</ref>在整个10月冲突一直在持续，反对派、政府军和平民都有死伤。<ref>{{cite web |author=October 8, 2012 |url=http://supportkurds.org/news/monday-8-october-2012/ |title=Monday 8 October 2012 : Support Kurds in Syria |publisher=Supportkurds.org |date=2012-10-08 |accessdate=2012-10-20 |archive-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025153524/http://supportkurds.org/news/monday-8-october-2012/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=October 12, 2012 |url=http://supportkurds.org/news/thursday-11-october-2012/ |title=Thursday 11 October 2012 : Support Kurds in Syria |publisher=Supportkurds.org |date=2012-10-12 |accessdate=2012-10-20 |archive-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025152845/http://supportkurds.org/news/thursday-11-october-2012/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=October 17, 2012 |url=http://supportkurds.org/news/tuesday-16-october-2012/ |title=Tuesday 16 October 2012 : Support Kurds in Syria |publisher=Supportkurds.org |date=2012-10-16 |accessdate=2012-10-20 |archive-date=2016-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405211838/http://supportkurds.org/news/tuesday-16-october-2012/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在10月25日<ref>{{cite web |url =http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/10/201210258572215445.html |title =Syria violence flares ahead of possible truce |publisher =[[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]] |date =2012-10-25 |accessdate =2012-10-25 |archive-date =2019-02-20 |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20190220062836/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/10/201210258572215445.html |dead-url =no }}</ref>及26日<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-fg-syria-truce-violence-20121027,0,4500176.story |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2012-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108102625/http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-fg-syria-truce-violence-20121027,0,4500176.story |dead-url=no }}</ref>，反对派在大马士革郊区的Harasta占领了两处政府军检查站，政府军则使用坦克和火箭炮攻击Harasta。

10月31日，FSA宣称他们获得了一支由反对阿萨德的巴勒斯坦人组成的武装派别的支持，这支部队称暴风旅（Storm Brigade），已经被武装起来以控制难民营。[[解放巴勒斯坦人民陣線總指揮部|解放巴勒斯坦人民陣線總指揮部]]（PFLP-GC）领导人[[艾哈迈德·贾布里勒|艾哈迈德·贾布里勒]]（Ahmed Jibril）和他的手下被指责骚扰营内的居民并攻击FSA武装分子。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.aljazeera.com/topic/syria/rebels-form-brigade-damascus-fight-armed-palestinians-aligned-president-assad |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304054022/http://blogs.aljazeera.com/topic/syria/rebels-form-brigade-damascus-fight-armed-palestinians-aligned-president-assad |dead-url=no }}</ref>许多来自难民营的巴勒斯坦人也加入了其他FSA部队并在大马士革的Tadamon区和Al-Hajar Al-Aswad区与FSA并肩作战。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2012/Jul-18/181033-palestinians-join-syria-revolt-activists-fsa.ashx#axzz2Aniktc00 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2017-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171214225837/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2012/Jul-18/181033-palestinians-join-syria-revolt-activists-fsa.ashx#axzz2Aniktc00 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在10月30日，反对派暗杀了叙利亚空军高级将领Abdullah Mahmoud al-Khalidi。之后的一周时间内，反对派更多的尝试暗杀政府方面的高价值目标。11月6日，反对派在Mohammed Osama Laham上班路上将其刺杀，他是叙利亚议会发言人的兄弟。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ottawacitizen.com/news/Syrian+Speaker+brother+killed/7508940/story.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2013-01-31 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130131020159/http://www.ottawacitizen.com/news/Syrian+Speaker+brother+killed/7508940/story.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

==反对派的攻势==
===11月份的冲突===

11月7日，反对派在大马士革市中心发动了一次大规模行动。反对派向总统官邸附近的[[阿拉维派|阿拉维派]]聚居的Mezzah区发射迫击炮弹，击中了总理办公室和Mezzah区的军用机场，导致3名平民丧生，12人受伤。大马士革革命委员会一名发言人Susan Ahmed称此次行动是“倒计时”，并声称“在这个地区正在发生一些严重的事情，并且事态正在失去控制。政府军再也不能控制大马士革了。”<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-20238859 Syria rebels attack Assad strongholds in Damascus] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-20238859 |date=20130513183402 }}, 2012-11-08.</ref>同一天，一名叙利亚大法官在大马士革居住区遭到暗杀。他的汽车下被安放了炸弹且炸弹是被遥控引爆的。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/story/2012/11/07/syria-judge-killed.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2013-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130102182428/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/story/2012/11/07/syria-judge-killed.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

11月12日，在大马士革东郊的古塔地区双方激烈交火，导致10名政府军和1名反对派武装丧生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=456097 |title=Deadly fighting near Damascus, Syrian border town bombed 12 November 2012 |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2017-10-09 |archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20171009185346/https://now.mmedia.me/lb/ar |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

11月17日，在大马士革郊区，一架政府军直升机被击落。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.aljazeera.com/topic/syria/sohr-rebels-down-helicopter-damascus |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2014-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140903052056/http://blogs.aljazeera.com/topic/syria/sohr-rebels-down-helicopter-damascus |dead-url=no }}</ref>

反对派在11月末加大了对大马士革的攻势。11月19日，在大马士革南大门的Hajar al-Aswad区反对派夺取了一处政府军部队的指挥部，这是反对派控制的距离大马士革市中心最近的一处军事基地。<ref name="ThReut_19Nov2012_alAswadbase">{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/11/19/syria-crisis-base-idUSL5E8MJJ8B20121119 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2014-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140129073621/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/11/19/syria-crisis-base-idUSL5E8MJJ8B20121119 |dead-url=no }}</ref>11月25日，反对派控制了位于东古塔地区的Marj al-Sultan空军基地，在战斗中两架政府军直升机被击落。<ref name="BBC_EGhouta_airbase_25nov2012">[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-20487492 Syria rebels 'seize Marj al-Sultan base near Damascus'] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-20487492 |date=20171011141814 }}, 2012-11-25.</ref>

11月28日，反对派武装进攻[[大马士革国际机场|大马士革国际机场]]，试图削弱政府军的空中优势。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2012/11/28/car-bombs-syria/1731267/ |title=Syrian rebels battling for Damascus airport 29 November 2012 |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2018-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180131000149/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2012/11/28/car-bombs-syria/1731267/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>11月29日，反对派声称他们已经阻断了通往机场的道路。<ref name="ThReut_Damas_airport29Nov2012">{{cite news | first=Oliver | last=Holmes | coauthors=Dominic Evans, Erika Solomon, Yasmine Saleh, Edmund Blair, Praveen Menon, Tabassum Zakaria,  David Alexander, Tarmo Virki, Justyna Pawlak, Tom Pfeiffer, Cynthia Osterman | pages= | language= | title=Fighting cuts access to Damascus airport, flights suspended | date=2012-11-29 | publisher=Thomson Reuters | url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/11/29/us-syria-crisis-idUSBRE8AJ1FK20121129 | accessdate=2012-11-30 | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6CY05FMb1?url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/11/29/us-syria-crisis-idUSBRE8AJ1FK20121129 | archivedate=2012-11-29 | deadurl=no }}</ref>叙利亚新闻部长声称通往机场的道路依旧安全并且没有反对派武装活动。埃及航空和阿联酋航空暂停了飞往大马士革的航班。<ref name="ThReut_Damas_airport29Nov2012" />[[BBC|BBC]]报道政府军在11月29日针对城东的反对派控制区发动了一场前所未有的攻势。

===12月初的冲突===

12月1日，大马士革东部的Arbin发生冲突。叙利亚人权观察组织（SOHR）报道，政府军向Zabadani炮击，导致多人受伤。政府军在Mliha与反对派战斗以试图保证通往机场的高速公路的安全。<ref name="perthnow_rifdim2dec2012">[http://www.perthnow.com.au/news/world/regime-forces-hammer-damascus-outskirts/story-fnd14032-1226528448648 Regime forces hammer rebels on Damascus outskirts 2 December 2012] {{Wayback|url=http://www.perthnow.com.au/news/world/regime-forces-hammer-damascus-outskirts/story-fnd14032-1226528448648 |date=20130526192103 }}</ref>

在通往机场的高速公路及其周边，双方的激烈交战以及政府军的轰炸持续至12月2日。当天埃及航空宣布在次日重开飞往大马士革国际机场的航班。政府军使用战机和火箭炮轰炸大马士革郊区反对派控制的地区，在阻止反对派接近大马士革的战斗中政府军击毙了至少10名反对派武装，并打伤了数十人。政府军进入了德拉雅的部分地区，在该地反对派曾使用迫击炮炮击大马士革市。政府军攻入了该镇的一端但反对派仍控制着该地区其他部分并向政府军回击。<ref>{{cite news |title=Syrian forces pound Damascus suburbs, flights to resume |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/12/02/us-syria-crisis-idUSBRE8AJ1FK20121202 |last=Solomon |first=Erica |publisher=Reuters |date=2 December 2012 |accessdate=3 December 2012 |archive-date=2013-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202221440/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/12/02/us-syria-crisis-idUSBRE8AJ1FK20121202 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

12月3日，叙利亚政府军继续使用火炮和战机针对大马士革附近的反对派控制区进行轰炸。<ref>{{cite news |title=Syria bombs Damascus suburbs, Putin in Ankara talks |url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5iaL6HAw7u0dWI2nh9BBkVwaCn4bg?docId=CNG.c19a448143681e6e4aeace3a0218a1cb.51 |publisher=[[Agence_France-Presse|Agence France-Presse]] |date=3 December 2012 |accessdate=3 December 2012 |archive-date=2013-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130407095245/http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5iaL6HAw7u0dWI2nh9BBkVwaCn4bg?docId=CNG.c19a448143681e6e4aeace3a0218a1cb.51 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

12月4日，叙利亚国家电视台报道反对派向大马士革郊区发射迫击炮，导致29名学生和一名老师丧生。<ref>{{cite news |title=Syrian rebels kill 29 students in attack on school near Damascus |url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/syria-29-students-killed-mortar-attack-17872899#.UL4YQuT8KW0 |last=Surk |first=Barbara |publisher=[[ABC_News|ABC News]] |date=4 December 2012 |accessdate=4 December 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121207002815/http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/syria-29-students-killed-mortar-attack-17872899#.UL4YQuT8KW0 |archive-date=2012-12-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

12月5日，靠近大马士革国际机场的Aqraba军用机场发生战斗，反对派声称已经控制了机场。

12月7日，反对派声称他们仍封锁着通往大马士革国际机场的大部分道路。大马士革军事委员会发言人Nabil al-Amir声称反对派“已经等待了两周以使得大部分平民和民用飞机撤出机场。到了12月7日，这座机场已经成为军事区，任何想要靠近它的平民将要自己承担风险。通往该机场的外国航班依旧暂停。一名政府方面的发言人声称政府军“已经迫使反对派退回了大马士革郊区和周边地区。”12月8日，通往机场的道路一度被封锁。

12月9日，政府军的反攻开始成功减轻了反对派对首都的压力。Patrick Cockburn在《独立报》上撰文声称政府军通过将军队从叙利亚农村地区调往大马士革加强了对首都的控制力度。一名与Patrick Cockburn有联系的外交官员声称；“在私底下，FSA的指挥官承认他们针对大马士革的进攻并没有按照计划进行，并且他们遭受了巨大损失，但这不意味着他们不会再次采取类似行动。”<ref name="Indep_govt_defends_Dam">{{cite news | first=Patrick | last=Cockburn | pages= | language= | title=Assad's strategy shift keeps rebels at gates of Damascus | date=2012-12-09 | publisher=The Independent | url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/assads-strategy-shift-keeps-rebels-at-gates-of-damascus-8397542.html | accessdate=2012-12-11 | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6CqDVcTyk?url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/assads-strategy-shift-keeps-rebels-at-gates-of-damascus-8397542.html | archivedate=2012-12-11 | deadurl=no | location=London }}</ref>有目击者声称看到通往机场的道路两旁躺着冲突双方战死者的尸体。一名接受纽约时报采访的反对派武装分子声称这对机场的进攻使得政府军分散兵力，使得那些试图攻占大马士革通往叙利亚东北地区道路的武装分子撤退。这些武装分子由于对战斗计划没有深思熟虑而遭受了严重损失。根据这名反对派的说法，政府军的反攻不可思议的猛烈。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/12/10/world/middleeast/syria-fighting-damascus.html?pagewanted=all |title=Fighting Drives an Old Sense of Peace From Damascus |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2013-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130610033509/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/12/10/world/middleeast/syria-fighting-damascus.html?pagewanted=all |dead-url=no }}</ref>

12月15日，一名反对派武装Ababil Horan和Eastern Ghouta旅的发言人声称叙利亚自由军袭击了大马士革的一个会议现场，打死多名负责政府军在大马士革及其郊区行动的官员。现在他们已经有能力知晓大马士革其他政府军行动指挥官的行动和会议内容。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2012/12/15/world/meast/syria-civil-war/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2014-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107010325/http://edition.cnn.com/2012/12/15/world/meast/syria-civil-war |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===雅穆克难民营冲突===
{{main|雅穆克难民营冲突}}

12月16日，叙利亚政府军的战机空袭了难民营，这是内战爆发以来的第一次。活动人士报道战机至少发射了两枚火箭弹，一座安置有从首都其他交战区逃离的难民的清真寺被击中，数十人丧生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/12/16/syria-crisis-camp-idUSL5E8NG4DX20121216 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924172612/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/12/16/syria-crisis-camp-idUSL5E8NG4DX20121216 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

12月17日，反对派声称营内的许多PFLP-GC武装分子投靠到了反对派阵营，而他们的领导人[[艾哈迈德·贾布里勒|艾哈迈德·贾布里勒]]和其余PFLP-GC武装分子加入了营外的政府军阵营。当天晚些时候反对派武装在反对阿萨德的巴勒斯坦人的帮助下完全控制了[[雅穆克难民营|雅穆克难民营]]及另一座巴勒斯坦难民营，将亲政府的PFLP-GC武装分子赶了出来。<ref>{{cite news|title=WRAPUP 1-Syrian rebels take control of Damascus Palestinian camp|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/12/17/syria-crisis-idUSL5E8NHGZZ20121217|accessdate=18 December 2012|newspaper=Reuters|date=17 December 2012|archive-date=2013-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203010736/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/12/17/syria-crisis-idUSL5E8NHGZZ20121217|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-20766628 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2018-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180917211730/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-20766628 |dead-url=no }}</ref>但是政府军已经完全包围了难民营，大量难民逃离家园。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/12/2012121717419248502.html|title=Syrian forces surround Palestinian camp|date=17 December 2012|publisher=Al Jazeera English|accessdate=18 December 2012|archive-date=2018-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180801034437/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/12/2012121717419248502.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

12月19日，雅穆克难民营外围发生新的战斗，1名平民和4名PFLP-GC成员丧生。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/12/20/256099.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012年12月20日 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121220133117/http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/12/20/256099.html |archivedate=2012年12月20日 |df= }}</ref>

12月24日，反对派伏击并击毙了Jaramana区的军事情报机构领导人，Jaramana区位于大马士革东南，居民以基督徒和德鲁兹派为主。

===德拉雅攻势===

12月31日，政府军加强了对反对派控制的德拉雅的炮击。政府军在镇外集结了一支大规模部队准备突袭该镇。<ref>{{cite news|title=Syrian Military Mounts Offensive in Suburb of Damascus|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/01/01/world/middleeast/syrian-military-mounts-offensive-in-damascus-suburb.html|accessdate=1 January 2013|newspaper=New York Times|date=31 December 2012|archive-date=2014-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140923140912/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/01/01/world/middleeast/syrian-military-mounts-offensive-in-damascus-suburb.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>反对派说政府军的一支装甲部队试图攻入德拉雅，但被叙利亚自由军击退。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.jpost.com/MiddleEast/Article.aspx?id=297908 |title=Assad's forces push to retake Damascus suburb |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2013-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130114090228/http://www.jpost.com/MiddleEast/Article.aspx?id=297908 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年1月2日，政府军的空袭击中了大马士革郊区Mleiha的一处加油站，导致70人丧生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-20890108 |title=Syria: Deadly air strike 'hits Damascus petrol station' |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2013-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130319180344/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-20890108 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1月4日，政府军继续进攻，使用地面部队和空军对大马士革郊外的反对派据点进行炮击和轰炸。反对派在首都郊外三个方向与政府军交战。但是，反对派的推进由于政府军持续的空袭而停滞不前。<ref>{{cite news |title=Syrian warplanes bomb suburbs of the capital as troops and rebels fight across the country |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/government-airstrikes-on-rebel-held-suburbs-show-limits-of-opposition-push-to-take-damascus/2013/01/03/efdbef0c-561c-11e2-89de-76c1c54b1418_story.html |newspaper=washingtonpost. |date=2013-01-04 |accessdate=2013-01-04 |archive-date=2013-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130104214110/http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/government-airstrikes-on-rebel-held-suburbs-show-limits-of-opposition-push-to-take-damascus/2013/01/03/efdbef0c-561c-11e2-89de-76c1c54b1418_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>一个报道政府军在大马士革郊外作战的国际记者团遭遇交火，一名[[路透社|路透社]]记者受伤。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://rt.com/news/rt-journalist-damascus-crossfire-318/ |title=RT correspondent injured in Damascus crossfire |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2014-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228235326/http://rt.com/news/rt-journalist-damascus-crossfire-318/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1月12日，一名政府军军官和一名SOHR的官员都证实政府军进入了德拉雅镇的大部分地区，镇内仍有激烈交火发生。<ref name=strategic>{{Cite web |url=http://www.canada.com/news/Syrian+army+advances+strategic+Damascus+suburb+rebels+gain+ground/7812604/story.html |title=Syrian army advances in strategic Damascus suburb as rebels gain ground in the north |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2013-02-15 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130215165242/http://www.canada.com/news/Syrian+army+advances+strategic+Damascus+suburb+rebels+gain+ground/7812604/story.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bostonglobe.com/news/world/2013/01/13/syrian-troops-capture-much-daraya-after-rebels-seize-air-base/nVeByO2T0LnvACKPxb4sSL/story.html |title=Syrian troops recapture key territory |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025150427/http://www.bostonglobe.com/news/world/2013/01/13/syrian-troops-capture-much-daraya-after-rebels-seize-air-base/nVeByO2T0LnvACKPxb4sSL/story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1月19日，据报道反对派武装仍控制着德拉雅市的部分地区。反对派武装还宣称在该市一名米格战斗机的飞行员叛变并用战机轰炸了该地区的三处政府军阵地，造成15名士兵丧生。但这一消息无法得到证实。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.aljazeera.com/liveblog/topic/syria-153 |title=Syria Live Blog |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304071334/http://blogs.aljazeera.com/liveblog/topic/Syria-153 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.itv.com/news/2013-01-19/damascus-loses-inhabitants-at-alarming-rate/ |title=Damascus suburb pounded to dust in deadly battle |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019065136/http://www.itv.com/news/2013-01-19/damascus-loses-inhabitants-at-alarming-rate/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1月24日，政府军从大马士革西侧向德拉雅市炮击。<ref>{{cite web||||}}</ref>

